===Etymology===
Coined by Sylvia Wright in ''[[w:Harper's Magazine|Harper’s Magazine]]'' (''The Death of Lady Mondegreen'', Nov 1954) from a mishearing of a line in the Scottish ballad ''The Bonny Earl of Murray'': "They hae slay the Earl of Murray, / And laid him on the green" (misheard as “Lady Mondegreen”).

